  "instructions": [
    "Preheat broiler.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together coconut cream, peanut butter, lime juice, soy sauce, brown sugar, garlic, ginger, red pepper flakes, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the chicken to the bowl and toss to coat with the creamy sauce.",
    "Arrange the chicken on a broiler pan lined with parchment paper.",
    "Broil for 5-7 minutes per side, or until the chicken is cooked through.",
    "Let the chicken rest for 5 minutes before serving.",
    "Serve the chicken hot with additional creamy sauce spooned over the top."
